      <body>I'm really not a fan of this auto-setting of locals. I think setting the counter local is already kinda fishy, but at least it's something that would otherwise be kinda hard. Setting the size of the collection is perfectly doable through current means, so I don't think it's worth the magic spell to do it automatically.

You're of course always free to turn it into a plugin ;)</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;I'm really not a fan of this auto-setting of locals. I think setting the counter local is already kinda fishy, but at least it's something that would otherwise be kinda hard. Setting the size of the collection is perfectly doable through current means, so I don't think it's worth the magic spell to do it automatically.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You're of course always free to turn it into a plugin ;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
